{
  "name": "subs_5",  
  "captions": [
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- Will this one survive?",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:05.640"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- It's probably too early to tell.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:10.500"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- But there is hope.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:13.470"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- There's always hope.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:15.648"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- This technology has the potential",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:19.140"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "to bring hope to millions.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:21.210"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "With its power, we can make interventions",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:24.630"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "in ways we previously only dreamt of.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:27.060"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "Because the process of screening\nand editing our children",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:30.900"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "not only allows us to hunt down reasons",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:34.350"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "that cause a life to end too soon,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:36.810"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "it can help us to find and\nprevent the genetic diseases",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:40.470"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "and abnormalities that will\naffect their later life.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:44.490"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "For example, there is a particular gene",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:49.290"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "that if it is carried by the\nparent and passed to the child,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:51.690"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "that child will have an\nextraordinarily high chance",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:55.800"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "of developing breast cancer.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:00:59.100"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- Very few of us carry those genes",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:01.890"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- Still.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:06.000"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "Could you imagine just for a minute,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:06.840"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "sitting with your child,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:09.270"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "suffering through\nprocedure after procedure",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:11.160"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "with a disease caused",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:13.503"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "by the genetic material you gave to them",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:15.300"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "that you choose to do nothing about?",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:18.990"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- I would assume, in most of these cases,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:26.700"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "an intervention could be made\nlater in their development.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:29.910"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- What do you mean by that?",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:33.990"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- Well, if I'm right,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:36.930"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "in this example,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:39.270"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "we are talking about\naltered versions of BRCA1,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:41.040"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "although it could be various others.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:47.370"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "Variants of these genes\ncan increase the risk",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:52.350"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "of getting breast cancer,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:56.280"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "but there are options one can\ntake once a child is born.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:01:58.830"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- That may be, but why take the risk?",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:03.240"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "Surely, it's better to\nensure they cannot happen",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:06.900"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "in the first place.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:08.790"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- Well, from a medical perspective,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:10.290"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "I can certainly see the benefits\nof using genetic editing",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:14.100"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "to eliminate serious congenital diseases",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:18.510"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "or high-risk mutations before\na foetus reaches full term.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:21.600"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "But, these conditions that\nwe talk of can vary hugely",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:26.580"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "in terms of the effects\non a person's life,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:32.130"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "their presentation, and\nseverity of symptoms.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:35.460"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "If we cannot accurately predict the impact",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:40.740"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "of eliminating or changing one's genes,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:44.550"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "then we could not\nethically make the decision",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:48.540"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "to make those alterations.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:52.500"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- I think we are overcomplicating this.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:54.510"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "Remember, an intervention of this nature",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:57.030"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "stops the potential of\nsomething cruel and painful",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:02:59.460"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "before it even has the\nchance to manifest itself.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:03.480"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "It will not stop all cancers,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:07.050"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "but imagine for those\nparents that carry risk",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:08.490"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "how freeing it could be to remove it.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:11.910"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- But as I said before, at this stage,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:14.340"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "parents would be calculating risk",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:17.100"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "and making decisions\non a percentage chance",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:19.200"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "of something possibly\nhappening way in the future.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:21.870"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "Decisions a child would not have a say in.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:26.460"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- In these cases,\npercentage or no percentage,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:29.040"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "surely the impact of our\ninaction will have more risk",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:31.770"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "than any action we could take.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:35.040"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- No one can dispute cancer is.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:39.510"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "And passing a gene hidden\nin our own genetic code",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:43.260"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "that poses them risk is.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:47.700"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "It feels natural to try and protect one",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:52.980"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "from such illnesses we could pass on them.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:03:56.670"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "But to talk about making a change now",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:00.240"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "to potentially save their life",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:03.750"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "in five, 10, 50, 80\nyears from now is just...",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:05.550"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- I'd say it comes down to",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:11.910"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "if you feel you should\nmake these decisions",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:14.520"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "not fully knowing what\nthe consequences would be,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:17.280"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "or you wait",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:21.540"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "to make an intervention.\n- When it could be too late.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:23.100"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "When it could be too late.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:25.444"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- When the level of risk\ncould be better understood.",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:29.730"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "- Would you want to remove genes",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:37.020"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "from your child that might\npose them a risk in the future,",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:39.570"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "or would you prefer to give them some role",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:45.390"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "in this decision later in life",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:48.090"
      },
      {
        "duration": 0,
        "content": "if that was possible?",
        "startOfParagraph": null,
        "startTime": "00:04:51.930"
      }
    ]
  }